n: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181228121757BoL5cng9HPJeIVMa.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.294498\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181228121758W45uMReHQS31nxf7.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.294498\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181228121804uTEDClBHFJKPrtgZ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.294498\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181228121801X57uGl39iDmBFQpv.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.294498\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201812281218104JkHadxS8n2bmU7s.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499531\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201812281218175pLihXgZlDnHomM1.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.294498\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181228121833HOETSdewAj3li1tx.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.294498\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181228121809fKaDJcv8P3E2n1lS.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.772500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181228121726Xap3BwcKSCbY8qZz.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.772500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181228121644LKnTdc76S0DNWqy3.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181228121738is2y3qCROmYa7D68.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"http://www.anothermag.com/fashion-beauty/11385/ten-moments-in-fashion-which-defined-2018\" rel=\"nofollow\"><em>Another Magazine</em> 整理回顾了 2018 年时尚行业最重要的 10 个瞬间。</a></strong><br></p><p>1. Kim Jones 成为 Dior 男装创意总监</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181228122812ztMi81LngyGIqcUj.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.252236\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>2. Hedi Slimane 发布他在 Celine 的第一个系列。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181228122942OmaL3Dk5Wg7ItxQZ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.496788\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>3. Valentino 创意总监 Pierpaolo Piccioli 获 2018 年英国时尚大奖 (British Fashion Awards) 年度设计师奖。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181228123234QwUbAeSM4HvghryO.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667939\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>4. Gucci、Versace、Burberry、DKNY、Chanel 以及 John Galliano 等均宣布放弃使用皮草。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181228123556LNPrmJMFvqcKuyQd.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.249057\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>5、纪梵希创意总监&nbsp;Clare Waight Keller 为&nbsp;Meghan Markle 与哈里王子大婚设计礼服。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181228123918fsw3Sze9O8oq4bhJ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>6、纪梵希创始人&nbsp;Hubert de Givenchy 去世，享年 91 岁。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181228124124Gp4CAgmiDkXQfybI.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.994318\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>7、Riccardo Tisci 成为 Burberry 创意总监。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201812281242256qvux4elth51Vwnc.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498929\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>8、Tyler Mitchell 成为第一位为美国版 Vogue 拍摄 9 月刊封面的黑人摄影师，年仅 23 岁。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201812281244199r6GoXOzQwLaDHUp.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.208333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>9、<em>“天赐美体：时尚与天主教意象（Heavenly Bodies: Fashion and the Catholic Imagination）”</em>成为纽约大都会艺术博物馆（Met）成立以来观展人数最多的展览。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201812281247540YNeHaKdTBQD3GyF.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.603053\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>10、英国时尚传奇人物&nbsp;Judy Blame 去世，享年 58 岁。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201812281249482ams5pXeLMBuFNjv.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.257194\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><br></p><p>题图来自&nbsp;<em>Metal Magazine</em> 造型特辑“<a href=\"https://metalmagazine.eu/en/post/editorial/three-girls-and-one-boy-guen-fiore\" rel=\"nofollow\">Three girls and one boy</a>”（三个女孩一个男孩）<strong>，</strong>摄影师 Guen Fiore，造型师 Julie Liu。</p>"}